          "_name": "team2",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"team2\" group=\"Team\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/html\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"fullWidth\" title=\"Full Width\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"2\" max=\"6\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Transparent\" name=\"transparentCard\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"cardBg\" value=\"#f7f7f7\" condition=\"!transparentCard\">\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\" selected>1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n        </select>\n        <header condition=\"showSocial\">Social</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Social\" name=\"showSocial\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"socialCount\" title=\"Count\" min=\"1\" max=\"5\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\" condition=\"showSocial\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"socialIconColor\" value=\"#6592e6\" condition=\"showSocial\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f7f7f7\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#cebfaf\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"item features-image\">\n            <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/flavio-vicente-psicologo2.png-1160x1160.png\" alt=\"Flávio Vicente Psicólogo Clínico\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style m-0 mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><br><b>Sobre mim</b></h5>\n                            <h6 class=\"card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-subtitle\">\n                                CRP XXX-XXXXX</h6>\n                            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .social-row\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">Sou<b> Flávio Vicente,</b> psicólogo clínico de orientação psicanalítica, atuo a partir da articulação entre teoria, pesquisa e clínica. Compreendo a análise como um espaço ético de elaboração, no qual o sujeito pode atribuir sentido às suas demandas e ressignificar sua relação consigo e com o mundo.<br><br>Minha prática se fundamenta no vínculo terapêutico, no manejo da transferência e na escuta rigorosa dos afetos.<br><br>Entendo a psicanálise como teoria do sujeito, ética da escuta e campo permanente de investigação, em diálogo com Freud, Ferenczi e Lacan.<br><br>Oriento meu trabalho pelo rigor teórico, responsabilidade ética, sigilo e recusa de promessas ou soluções imediatas.<br></p>\n                            <div class=\"social-row display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSocial\">\n                                <div class=\"soc-item\">\n                                    <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Mobirise/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon-instagram socicon\"></span>\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"soc-item\" mbr-if=\"socialCount>1\">\n                                    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mobirise\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon socicon-twitter\"></span>\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"soc-item\" mbr-if=\"socialCount>2\">\n                                    \n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon-instagram socicon\" style=\"font-size: 22px;\"></span>\n                                    \n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"soc-item\" mbr-if=\"socialCount>3\">\n                                    <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/mobirise\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon socicon-youtube\"></span>\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"soc-item\" mbr-if=\"socialCount>4\">\n                                    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mobirise\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon socicon-telegram\"></span>\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        \n    </div>\n</section>",
